        <abstract> 
<p>Samuel Butler’s fierce attack on CD and EK in <hi rend="italic">Athenæum</hi>. CD’s sentence saying that EK had altered his <hi rend="italic">Kosmos</hi> article was accidentally omitted from second proofs. Butler insinuates that EK’s attack on his book was suggested by CD or interpolated by him in EK’s text.</p> 
        </abstract>
